Package ru.postgrespro.perf.pgmicrobench.statanalyzer.distributions.recognition

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDistributionTest  
    IParameterEstimator  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CramerVonMises
    This class provides methods to perform the Cramer–Von Mises test for goodness of fit and to fit a distribution to a given dataset using the Cramer–Von Mises statistic.
    EstimatedParameters
    Represents a fitted distribution along with its parameters and p-value.
    FittedDistribution
    The FittedDistribution class represents a probability distribution that has been fitted to a dataset.
    KolmogorovSmirnov
    This class provides methods to perform the Kolmogorov-Smirnov test for goodness of fit and to fit a distribution to a given dataset using the Kolmogorov-Smirnov statistic.
    MaximumLikelihoodEstimation
    Class for estimating distribution parameters using the Maximum Likelihood Estimation (MLE) method.
    Multicriteria
    Multicriteria.
    Pearson
    The Pearson class provides implementation of Pearson's algorithm for fitting distributions and performing the Pearson goodness-of-fit test.
    Pearson.Bounds
